title: Rigney and Rosati named 2015 WVU Homecoming queen, king (West Virginia University)
text: ( Source : West Virginia University ) Blaire Rigney and Joe Rosati have been announced as West Virginia University's 2015 Homecoming king and queen. Rigney and Rosati were crowned during halftime of the WVU-Oklahoma State football game tonight
